{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"36004-erai-adiakaret-na-ikapa","title":"Erai Adiakaret na Ikapa","description":"Awaragat na ikamunit ikoku yen mam isomat aswam na ijaikitai nesi osomero. Auta ngesi aitetem iboro ejaikini nesi mam iswamai.","language":"Ateso","langCode":"teo","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Susan Acham"],"illustrators":["Priya Kuriyan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/36004-erai-adiakaret-na-ikapa"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/696669/size3/8717a72070ac52bd090aeebc8e6b36e6.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/696669/size6/8717a72070ac52bd090aeebc8e6b36e6.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13955/size6/74b224ec7927eb345bdc2c97d734e290.jpg","text":"Inyo mam ijo isomator aswam na ijaikitai ijo osomero?\nAjakait, erai adiakaret ikapa","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13956/size6/cd8835c2cbb54badb351efe4519e3c73.jpg","text":"Imam ngesi aiminaikin kuju okitoi, mam ti eongo alemunit alada adokia.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13957/size6/82dcc28b0ebb8f0b4d44834aefe31da9.jpg","text":"Arai mam eong alemunit alada adokia, mam ti eong etemonokit nesi.\nArai mam eong etemonik nesi, mam ti eong etwekenyunit ikoku.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13958/size6/cbebcafd09ccafb93a53ccbf97d5212d.jpg","text":"Arai mam eong etwekenyunit ikoku, mam ti totoka ekeru koipois.\nArai mam totoka ekerunit kopimbiro, mam ti edokolet elomunit togo.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13959/size6/6afe4b32d72fda92b47269657fdd7f5e.jpg","text":"Arai mam edokolet edokunit togo, mam ti ngesi enyamarit inyamat keere.\nArai mam ngesi enyamarit inyamat keere, mam papaka ti egwelunit akokor na ipoitai cut koiduuka.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13960/size6/47a620ff87a41f00183aa5c5d6ef823d.jpg","text":"Arai mam papaka egwelunit akokor naipoitai cut koiduka, mam ti ekingok etupu nesi ore.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13961/size6/46fe6dae5591c1691562f296e5ec8e86.jpg","text":"Arai mam ekingok etupunit ngesi ore, mam ti enyamarit aswam na ejaikitai eong kosomero.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13962/size6/5859bccb9c8b5fd5f6d2056c1ebeb45c.jpg","text":"Ibala do ijo ebe obu ekingok onyama aswam?","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13965/size6/50392cc21b95981389adaae52caf3f30.jpg","text":"Eebo, Ajakait, erai adiakaret ikapa!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":9,"words":132}}